Item 1
The Exclusive Club at Hammock Beach
Join Membership
Discover the allure of The Club at Hammock Beach - home to six Signature oceanfront golf holes and an unmatched coastal lifestyle. Enjoy unlimited access to a wealth of premium amenities and benefits, and immerse yourself in a vibrant, thriving community that embraces the vacation lifestyle year-round. As a member, you'll experience privileges that go beyond those offered to resort guests, including access to private events and special discounts.
For more information or to schedule a personal tour, please contact the Membership Office at
888.252.6294
or email
hb.membership@hammockbeach.com
. Discover what makes membership at The Club at Hammock Beach truly exceptional.
Request Information
Featured Builders Program
One-mile beach Club featuring beach chair service
Two award winning Signature golf courses, with amenities
8 hydro-grid clay tennis courts and four decoturf pickleball courts, with pro shop and expert instruction
The Spa at Hammock Beach, offering massages, facials and body treatments, as welll as hair and nail services
Three athletic centers, 50+ weekly fitness classes and nine swimming pools including a lazy river and three-story water slide
​ Exceptional restaurants ranging from casual to fine dining
​ Kids Crew at Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa
available for ages 4-12
​ Members only special events and activities
​ No assessments
​ Competitive dues structure
​ Golf memberships available upon request
​ Access to all resort activities
Featured Builders Program
​Embarking on a journey to build or purchase your dream home within the prestigious Hammock Beach community is made seamless with our curated selection of preferred builders and realtors. These esteemed professionals are renowned for their commitment to excellence.
Learn More
Testimonials
Now retired, we spend our days enjoying everything Hammock Beach has to offer - the beach, community events, pickleball and golfing, and above all, the friendships we've built. Life here is full, vibrant, and never boring.
- Eileen W
Hammock Beach didn't just give us a new address - it gave us a place where our entire family could be together, thrive, and feel truly at home. We are forever grateful.
- Chip G
My husband, Roger, and I flew from our then-home - Cincinnati - to visit the area, and we instantly fell in love with Hammock Beach, and purchase a lot. We were still involved in our careers, but knew we had discovered our future forever home. A few years later, we moved, built a house, and became members of the Club. And, here we are, members for 18 years, and waking up every day happy that we live here and that we are members of the Club at Hammock Beach.
- Jan C
Being in the rental progream with two units now, I truly believe buying here and becoming members is one of the smartest things I've ever done!
- Pamela B

Customized Experiences for Every Group
Teambuilding Activities
Strengthen bonds and create lasting memories with our dynamic teambuilding activities, perfect for groups of all types, from corporate meetings to family reunions. Tailored to inspire collaboration and fun, these activities can be booked to suit your group's unique needs. Our teambuilding activities are crafted to meet the unique needs of your group. From engaging challenges to collaborative tasks, we ensure that each experience promotes unity and enjoyment. Let us help you create an unforgettable event that brings your team closer together in a relaxed and inspiring environment.
Strengthen Connections
At Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa, we offer dynamic teambuilding activities designed to foster collaboration and create lasting memories. Whether you're organizing a corporate meeting or a family reunion, our programs are tailored to inspire teamwork and fun. Set against the backdrop of our oceanfront resort, these activities provide the perfect setting to strengthen bonds and enhance group cohesion.

Submit Inquiry
The Ideal Place To Host Your Next Event
Meetings & Events
Voted "Best On-Site Support Staff" by Smart Meetings in 2019, and one of "4 U.S. Beach Destinations for Meetings and Events That Deliver" by Meetings Today in 2023, Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa is the perfect place to host your next meeting or event. At Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa, activities abound and the full-service recreation department can assist in making your meeting or event an unforgettable experience for your guests.
See Floor Plans
Fact Sheet
12,000+ Square Foot Indoor Function Space
50,000 Square Feet of Indoor & Outdoor Event Space
Indoor, Outdoor & Oceanfront Venues
Incentives, Retreats, Golf Groups & more!
Lively Social Events
Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa is here to assist in planning your special event every step of the way. For showers, parties, dinners and all your social group needs, our event professionals provide the same level of service and detail whether your event is small or large.
Group Activities & Team-building
Go Team!
Teamwork makes the dream work! Host your upcoming team-building event at Hammock Beach Golf Resort & Spa. Your dedicated conference services manager will assist you in scheduling your event and our on-site recreation team will be there to make your event a successful one.
Team Building Activities
Making Ordinary Events Extraordinary
Day Meetings Package
Book a day meeting and receive one of the following perks: putting course team building, complimentary morning or afternoon refreshment break, 9 holes on the breathtaking Jack Nicklaus-designed Ocean Course at a preferred rate.
Meals They'll Remember
Banquet Menus
From Breakfast to Reception, from Break to Dinner, our Culinary Team is ready to whip up something that your guests will never forget! With flavorsome bites and stunning presentations, every meal is sure to make an impression.
Limited Time Group Offer
Savings & Hot Dates
'Tis the season to plan ahead! Whether you're hosting a holiday party, corporate retreat, or winter gathering, Hammock Beach offers the perfect oceanfront backdrop—and even better deals. Enjoy special group rates, value-packed perks, and limited-time hot dates to make your event unforgettable.
Reserve your holiday date
Oceanfront Venues Along the Atlantic Coast
Events & Occasions
Plan your next special occasions or corporate meeting with us and enjoy our newly renovated venues. We offer over 50,000 square feet of flexible indoor and outdoor event space across 11 acres, including a spectacular ballroom with over 4,500 square feet. Featuring a timeless design with all-new furnishings we are the ideal resort destination for your next event.
Banquet Menu 2024
